Package cytoscape.editor.actions

Class Summary
DeleteAction action for deleting selected Cytoscape nodes and edges
EdgeAction action assigned to Connect button on toolbar in CytoscapeEditor sets cursor to "edge cursor" and sets editor's mode to "CONNECT_MODE"
NewNetworkAction creates a new network and associates an editor with it
NodeAction action assigned to Add Node button on toolbar in CytoscapeEditor sets cursor to "add cursor" and sets editor's mode to "ADD_MODE"
RedoAction redo an operation that has been undone
SetEditorAction Assigns an editor for all NetworkViews in the Cytoscape environment.
UndoAction action called when user invokes "undo" operation
